===Noun===
{{cmn-noun|p|pint=biao3yan3|tas=琛ㄦ紨}}

# performance; exhibition

===Verb===
{{cmn-verb|p|pint=biao3yan3|tas=琛ㄦ紨}}

# to perform; to act; to play
# to demonstrate

